				<h1 id="intro">Introduction</h1>
				<p><strong>Pieuvre</strong> <em>&nbsp;[pj&oelig;v&#640;]</em> Pieuvre is the french word for octopus. You can learn more about this fantastic animal at <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Octopus">Wikipedia</a>.</p>

				<p>Today, the Internet provides so many sources of information, so many topics, so many different opinions, <em>etc.</em> It requires an important time to follow all this information.</p>

				<p>The Pieuvre aims to provide a new way of organising and reading information on/of the Internet.</p>

				<p><strong>The Pieuvre organises and finds the information for you, reading the Internet.</strong></p>

				<div class="alert alert-warning">
					<strong>Beta:</strong> The service is currently in beta. Features will be added as soon as they are developed. 
				</div>
				<hr>
				<h1 id ="skills">Features</h1>
				<p>All details about features are detailed in the <a href="${createLink(controller: 'welcome', action: 'help')}">help</a> (you need to be a member and logged in to access to the help).</p>
				<dl>
  					<dt>Following News</dt>
  					<dd>Internet is full of feeds and sites to follow. The Pieuvre follows the Internet for you.</dd>
  					<dt>Sorting News</dt>
  					<dd>Internet generates so much news that it is impossible for a human to follow all the desired information. The Pieuvre uses natural language processing for sorting news and saving times to humans.</dd>
  					<dt>Finding News</dt>
  					<dd>On Internet, humans need to know what they look for to find it. The Pieuvre finds what you are looking for before you think of it.</dd>
  					<dt>Reading News</dt>
  					<dd>Well, the Pieuvre loves reading news on Internet. As she does it all the time, she  helps you for faster and better reading.</dd>
  					<dt>Exploring News</dt>
  					<dd>Curious, the Pieuvre is. She is always eager to share her knowledge with you.</dd>
  					<dt>Sharing News</dt>
  					<dd>Obviously, Internet is all about sharing!</dd>
				</dl>
