				<h1 id="history">History</h1>
				<dl class="dl-horizontal">
  					<dt>September 2012</dt>
  					<dd>The emergence of an idea: Too many unread articles in Alex's Google Reader and the observation that the same news was often covered by several feeds. Then, why not sorting and grouping articles by similars?</dd>
  					<dt>December 2012</dt>
  					<dd>First lines of codes, in Groovy/Grails and Python of course!</dd>
  					<dt>January 2013</dt>
  					<dd>Acquisition of the domain name: thepieuvre.com</dd>
  					<dt>February 2013</dt>
  					<dd>Feed fetching and natural language processing are operationals enougth for having a simple version of the similar sorting algorithm. First demos to family and friends.</dd>
  					<dt>April 2013</dt>
  					<dd>First server for hosting the Pieuvre, a Kimsufi R-8G.</dd>
  					<dt>May 2013</dt>
