  					<dt>September 2013</dt>
  					<dd>A revamped UI based on Bootstrap 3.0.</dd>
  					<dt>September 2013</dt>
  					<dd>The Kimsufi R-8G is replaced by a Kimsufi KS 24G, same price more memory! Still a single machine for the whole hosting.</dd>
  					<dt>October 2013</dt>
